        <p class="audreysitepar">Visit the official website of Audrey Hepburn and the Audrey Hepburn Children's Fund.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="http://www.audreyhepburn.com/menu/index02.php" target="_blank">Visit the Site &raquo;</a></p>
